### AI Agent — REST Client requests
### Requires VS Code extension: humao.rest-client

@agentUrl = http://localhost:8000

# =============================================================================
# HEALTH & METRICS
# =============================================================================

### Health check
GET {{agentUrl}}/health

###

### Metrics
GET {{agentUrl}}/metrics

# =============================================================================
# AGENT — send messages and get replies
# =============================================================================

### Ask about products
POST {{agentUrl}}/api/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": "user-001",
  "message": "Hi! What products do you have?"
}

###

### Check order status
POST {{agentUrl}}/api/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": "user-001",
  "message": "Check order ORD-10001"
}

###

### Search electronics
POST {{agentUrl}}/api/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": "user-002",
  "message": "Show me electronics products"
}

###

### Ask about events
POST {{agentUrl}}/api/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": "user-003",
  "message": "What events are coming up?"
}
